headline: On National 811 Day, Consumers Energy Reminds Customers of Their Role in Natural Gas Safety
summary: Notice a strong rotten egg smell at your home or business? Planning to do some digging in your backyard? On National 811 Day, Consumers Energy is reminding customers of the steps they can take -- every day – to make sure everyone stays safe around natural gas in Michigan.
